with increased life expectancy, QALYs, and reduced complication incidences 
comparing with glimepiride. When the UK cost of liraglutide was discounted by 38 
percent, liraglutide would be a cost-effective option in China from the 
healthcare system perspective using the 3X GDP/capita per QALY as the WTP 
threshold.

